description: Developed a visually engaging and interactive front-end Crypto Dashboard using React and Chakra UI. The project emphasizes clean, modern UI design and intuitive user experience, providing users with a sleek interface to view and interact with cryptocurrency data.
Developed a responsive and interactive front-end clone of Twitter using TailwindCSS, focusing on replicating the user interface with a clean and efficient design.
Machine learning models can predict Autism Spectrum Disorder (ASD) by analyzing patterns and features in data, helping in early detection and personalized intervention strategies.
Created an engaging dice game using React, featuring interactive elements and dynamic game logic to enhance user experience and gameplay.
